51 static const std::string ROBOT_DESCRIPTION = "robot_description";
52 
53 int main(int argc, char** argv)
54 {
55  ros::init(argc, argv, "initialize_demo_db", ros::init_options::AnonymousName);
56 
57  boost::program_options::options_description desc;
58  desc.add_options()("help", "Show help message")("host", boost::program_options::value<std::string>(),
59  "Host for the "
60  "DB.")("port", boost::program_options::value<std::size_t>(),
61  "Port for the DB.");
62 
63  boost::program_options::variables_map vm;
64  boost::program_options::store(boost::program_options::parse_command_line(argc, argv, desc), vm);
65  boost::program_options::notify(vm);
66 
67  if (vm.count("help"))
68  {
69  std::cout << desc << std::endl;
70  return 1;
71  }
72  // Set up db
73  warehouse_ros::DatabaseConnection::Ptr conn = moveit_warehouse::loadDatabase();
74  if (vm.count("host") && vm.count("port"))
75  conn->setParams(vm["host"].as<std::string>(), vm["port"].as<std::size_t>());
76  if (!conn->connect())
77  return 1;
78 
79  ros::AsyncSpinner spinner(1);
80  spinner.start();
81 
82  ros::NodeHandle nh;
83  planning_scene_monitor::PlanningSceneMonitor psm(ROBOT_DESCRIPTION);
84  if (!psm.getPlanningScene())
85  {
86  ROS_ERROR("Unable to initialize PlanningSceneMonitor");
87  return 1;
88  }
89 
90  moveit_warehouse::PlanningSceneStorage pss(conn);
91  moveit_warehouse::ConstraintsStorage cs(conn);
92  moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage rs(conn);
93  pss.reset();
94  cs.reset();
95  rs.reset();
96 
97  // add default planning scenes
98  moveit_msgs::PlanningScene psmsg;
99  psm.getPlanningScene()->getPlanningSceneMsg(psmsg);
100  psmsg.name = "default";
101  pss.addPlanningScene(psmsg);
102  ROS_INFO("Added default scene: '%s'", psmsg.name.c_str());
103 
104  moveit_msgs::RobotState rsmsg;
105  moveit::core::robotStateToRobotStateMsg(psm.getPlanningScene()->getCurrentState(), rsmsg);
106  rs.addRobotState(rsmsg, "default");
107  ROS_INFO("Added default state");
108 
109  const std::vector<std::string>& gnames = psm.getRobotModel()->getJointModelGroupNames();
110  for (const std::string& gname : gnames)
111  {
112  const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg = psm.getRobotModel()->getJointModelGroup(gname);
113  if (!jmg->isChain())
114  continue;
115  const std::vector<std::string>& lnames = jmg->getLinkModelNames();
116  if (lnames.empty())
117  continue;
118 
119  moveit_msgs::OrientationConstraint ocm;
120  ocm.link_name = lnames.back();
121  ocm.header.frame_id = psm.getRobotModel()->getModelFrame();
122  ocm.orientation.x = 0.0;
123  ocm.orientation.y = 0.0;
124  ocm.orientation.z = 0.0;
125  ocm.orientation.w = 1.0;
126  ocm.absolute_x_axis_tolerance = 0.1;
127  ocm.absolute_y_axis_tolerance = 0.1;
128  ocm.absolute_z_axis_tolerance = boost::math::constants::pi<double>();
129  ocm.weight = 1.0;
130  moveit_msgs::Constraints cmsg;
131  cmsg.orientation_constraints.resize(1, ocm);
132  cmsg.name = ocm.link_name + ":upright";
133  cs.addConstraints(cmsg, psm.getRobotModel()->getName(), jmg->getName());
134  ROS_INFO("Added default constraint: '%s'", cmsg.name.c_str());
135  }
136  ROS_INFO("Default MoveIt Warehouse was reset.");
137 
138  ros::shutdown();
139 
140  return 0;
141 }
